php - This just installs a striped down version of PHP.
      It used to be for demoRunner but PHP is no longer
      used for demoRunner.  It uses nodejs instead.


# besides the GNU autotools we need re2c to build PHP:
apt-get install re2c

git clone https://github.com/php/php-src.git git


TO INSTALL:

1. run:

     ./php-VERSION/install.bash

